{"tid":1707484,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"仲有冇人琴晚嘅又一城同馬鞍山頌安","createTime":"2019-11-11T10:16:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T12:26:45.000Z","uid":242358,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"af73b84b14a8677b7c5bdd875d598d6318d1b1a6","tid":1707484,"uid":242358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T10:16:49.000Z","msg":"呢兩單嘢都好似冇咩人跟<br />\n1.又一城<br />\n琴晚狗突然封咗三樓<br />\n仲有疑似「鑑證科」/法醫出現<br />\n一定有古怪<br />\n停車場亦有離奇手印同血跡<br />\n<br />\n2.馬鞍山頌安頌智<br />\n有手足聽到個女仔叫救命<br />\n大概喺0055左右<br />\n<br />\n麻煩大家繼續留意下<br />\n我明白今日發生咗好多不幸嘅事<br />\n但呢兩單絕對唔可以唔理<br />\n<br />\n另外聽日繼續三罷<br />\n黎明行動2.0<br />\n 有跟開嘅手足就麻煩講聲"},{"pid":"94423e9bedf21feedbbcd93bcd5705a52e84ad51","tid":1707484,"uid":242358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T10:17:01.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"23e0cdbc1e322d4cc2fc472252d993ce8f859ecd","tid":1707484,"uid":242358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T10:17:11.000Z","msg":"唔可以唔理"},{"pid":"6ad4a34b772a133fc677da1601a5d30bace864d0","tid":1707484,"uid":242358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T10:18:00.000Z","msg":"我地冇咗好多手足架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16ab9e1f3bb73fe4d1dbd21326c5f65365a40ad0","tid":1707484,"uid":242358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T10:19:38.000Z","msg":"答我plz<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ea430acb85b8ed47eb777e3e6dac8c0c4ef14bf","tid":1707484,"uid":9542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T10:21:52.000Z","msg":"頌安琴日有手足落去睇左幾轉都無發現"},{"pid":"67f8aaa2e469872d683e68733d19b25572b6a737","tid":1707484,"uid":242358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4ea430acb85b8ed47eb777e3e6dac8c0c4ef14bf","tid":1707484,"uid":9542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T10:21:52.000Z","msg":"頌安琴日有手足落去睇左幾轉都無發現"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T1